Trigger { -- No comment (B7116B60)
	players = {P1},
	conditions = {
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 1, "Zerg Spawning Pool");
		Command(P5, AtLeast, 1, "Hyperion (Battlecruiser)");
		Bring(P7, AtLeast, 1, "울트라 좀비", "Location 6");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtMost, 0, "Zerg Overmind");
		Deaths(Force1, Exactly, 0, "Zerg Extractor");
		Switch("Switch 17", Set);
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		MoveLocation("Location 16", "울트라 좀비", P7, "Location 6");
		SetMemoryX(0x666458, SetTo, 0x0000014C, 65535);
		CreateUnit(1, "Scanner Sweep", "Location 16", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("Scanner Sweep", CurrentPlayer);
		PlayWAV("staredit\\wav\\skill1.wav");
		DisplayText("\x13\x03P - 지원사격", 4);
		ModifyUnitEnergy(1, "울트라 좀비", P7, "Location 16", 50);
		SetDeaths(P6, Add, 1, "Zeratul (Dark Templar)");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 2, "Zerg Extractor");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 133, "Zerg Overmind");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Easy Mode");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Lurker Egg");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Lurker");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Larva");
	},
}

	},
	actions = {

		PlayWAV("sound\\Protoss\\Darchon\\mind.wav");

		Deaths(P6, AtMost, 4, "Zerg Larva");
		Command(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 1, "군인 - 소총병");
		Bring(P12, AtLeast, 1, "폭탄을 든 좀비", "Location 21");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 3, "Zerg Spawning Pool");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtMost, 0, "Zerg Lurker Egg");
		Switch("Switch 17", Cleared);
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		PlayWAV("staredit\\wav\\skill3.WAV");
		SetMemoryX(0x666458, SetTo, 0x000000D5, 65535);
		CreateUnit(1, "Scanner Sweep", "Location 1", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("Scanner Sweep", CurrentPlayer);
		DisplayText("\x13\x03P - \x03회피", 0);
		SetInvincibility(Enable, "군인 - 소총병", CurrentPlayer, "Anywhere");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 100, "Zerg Hydralisk Den");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 216, "Zerg Lurker Egg");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Overmind");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Easy Mode");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Lurker");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Larva");
	},
}

		Deaths(P6, Exactly, 5, "Zerg Larva");
		Command(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 1, "군인 - 소총병");
		Bring(Force1, AtLeast, 1, "바이러스 가디언", "Location 29");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 3, "Zerg Spawning Pool");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtMost, 0, "Zerg Lurker Egg");
		Switch("Switch 17", Cleared);
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		PlayWAV("staredit\\wav\\skill3.WAV");
		SetMemoryX(0x666458, SetTo, 0x000000D5, 65535);
		CreateUnit(1, "Scanner Sweep", "Location 4", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("Scanner Sweep", CurrentPlayer);

Trigger { -- No comment (5AC2EFAA)
	players = {P1},
	conditions = {
		Deaths(P6, AtMost, 4, "Zerg Larva");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 2, "Zeratul (Dark Templar)");
		Command(P5, AtLeast, 1, "Hyperion (Battlecruiser)");
		Switch("Switch 17", Set);
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		SetMemoryX(0x666458, SetTo, 0x0000003A, 65535);
		CreateUnit(1, "Scanner Sweep", "Location 1", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("Scanner Sweep", CurrentPlayer);
		PlayWAV("staredit\\wav\\skill4.ogg");
		PlayWAV("staredit\\wav\\skill4.ogg");
		PlayWAV("staredit\\wav\\skill4.ogg");
		DisplayText("\x13\x03P - \x03Heal", 0);
		ModifyUnitHitPoints(1, "Hyperion (Battlecruiser)", P5, "Anywhere", 100);
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 0, "Zeratul (Dark Templar)");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 1071, "Zerg Lurker");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Overmind");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Easy Mode");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Lurker Egg");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Larva");
	},
}

Trigger { -- No comment (C7E0AEAE)
	players = {P1},
	conditions = {
		Deaths(P6, AtMost, 4, "Zerg Larva");
		Command(P5, AtLeast, 1, "Hyperion (Battlecruiser)");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 5, "Zerg Spawning Pool");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtMost, 0, "Zerg Larva");
		Bring(P7, AtLeast, 1, "Men", "Location 26");
		Switch("Switch 17", Set);
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		PlayWAV("sound\\Protoss\\TEMPLAR\\PTeHal00.WAV");
		PlayWAV("sound\\Protoss\\TEMPLAR\\PTeHal00.WAV");
		PlayWAV("sound\\Protoss\\TEMPLAR\\PTeHal00.WAV");
		CreateUnit(1, "분신 [1단계]", "Location 6", CurrentPlayer);
		CreateUnit(1, "분신 [2단계]", "Location 6", CurrentPlayer);
		MoveLocation("Location 46", "분신 [1단계]", CurrentPlayer, "Anywhere");
		MoveLocation("Location 51", "분신 [2단계]", CurrentPlayer, "Anywhere");
		SetMemoryX(0x666458, SetTo, 0x00000221, 65535);
		CreateUnit(1, "Scanner Sweep", "Location 46", CurrentPlayer);
		SetMemoryX(0x666458, SetTo, 0x00000221, 65535);
		CreateUnit(1, "Scanner Sweep", "Location 51", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("Scanner Sweep", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("분신 [1단계]", CurrentPlayer);
		RemoveUnit("분신 [2단계]", CurrentPlayer);
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 1189, "Zerg Larva");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Overmind");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Easy Mode");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Lurker Egg");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Add, 5, "Zerg Lurker");
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, SetTo, 2, "Vespene Tank (Terran Type 2)");

	conditions = {
		Deaths(P6, Exactly, 2, "Zerg Larva");
		Deaths(P6, AtLeast, 2132, "Terran Control Tower");
		Deaths(P6, AtMost, 2299, "Terran Control Tower");
		Bring(P6, AtMost, 0, "Zerg Zergling", "Location 91");
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		CreateUnitWithProperties(1, "Zerg Zergling", "Location 91", P6, {
			clocked = false,
			burrowed = true,
			intransit = false,
			hallucinated = false,
			invincible = true,
			hitpoint = 100,
			shield = 100,
			energy = 100,
			resource = 0,
			hanger = 0,
		});
		SetInvincibility(Enable, "Zerg Zergling", P6, "Location 85");
	},
}

		PlayWAV("sound\\Misc\\TRescue.wav");
		PlayWAV("sound\\Misc\\TRescue.wav");
		RemoveUnitAt(All, "Any unit", "Location 85", P12);
		RemoveUnitAt(All, "Any unit", "Location 85", AllPlayers);
		RemoveUnitAt(All, "플라잉 좀비충", "Location 120", P12);

	conditions = {
		Deaths(P6, Exactly, 5, "Zerg Larva");
		Switch("Switch 36", Set);
		Deaths(P6, AtMost, 999, "Gerard DuGalle (Ghost)");
		Deaths(P6, AtLeast, 505, "Gerard DuGalle (Ghost)");
		Deaths(P7, AtMost, 1999, "Zerg Hydralisk Den");
		Deaths(P7, AtLeast, 1036, "Zerg Hydralisk Den");
		Deaths(CurrentPlayer, AtLeast, 100, "Left Wall Flame Trap");
		Bring(CurrentPlayer, Exactly, 0, "군인 - 소총병", "Location 74");
	},
	actions = {
		PreserveTrigger();
		SetDeaths(CurrentPlayer, Subtract, 100, "Left Wall Flame Trap");
		ModifyUnitEnergy(All, "분신", Force1, "Location 74", 0);
		PlayWAV("sound\\Zerg\\Queen\\ZQuEns00.wav");
		PlayWAV("sound\\Zerg\\Queen\\ZQuEns00.wav");
		PlayWAV("sound\\Zerg\\Queen\\ZQuEns00.wav");
	},
